        "criticism": "It is critical to select the most engaging and relevant points for the Instagram audience, ensuring the summary is informative yet succinct, suitable for social media consumption.",
        "summaryforgpt": "Task: Make a post about Energy Harvesting for Wearable Technology. Actions taken: Visited IEEE Spectrum article and extracted key points, which were then added to memory with key 'KeyPointsEnergyHarvesting'. Next steps: Use these key points to craft the Instagram post summary and DALL-E 3 image generation. Additional URLs visited: https://spectrum.ieee.org/energy-harvesting-wearable-tech for in-depth content. Documents involved: 'energyHarvestingSearchResults.txt'."
    }
}

